Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.35,0:01:39.67,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,A rock concert I went to with Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:42.40,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HCDCCBC&\a5\fscx86\fscy82\pos(368,363)}Service suspended between\NShirai and Mikami,\Ndue to flooding on the tracks. \NThank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:46.64,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Because of a rainstorm, \Ntrain service stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:48.22,def2,.KUNIMI.,0,0,0,,...and many accidents followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:50.15,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HB6D4E9&\pos(309,120)}"Up-bound" train service\Nhas ended for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:53.45,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,We couldn't go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:59.01,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,...and we, Hikari and I, ended up in a scenario where we had to spend the night together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:12.70,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H712422&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fscx83\fscy87\frz1.645\pos(300,344)}Concert Site
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:45.39,def2,.WOMAN:.,0,0,0,,Welcome to our inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:50.00,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad we were able to find a nice inn, Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:53.00,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:06.02,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Well, there was the rainstorm, and then a childbirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:09.73,def2,.KUNIMI.,0,0,0,,In the end, we missed the last train.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:13.75,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,It really was awful today, Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:14.65,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:26.55,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,But the concert was great,\N so I guess it balances out.{was all right on balance.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:28.27,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Right, Big Sister ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.18,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:46.65,def2,.WOMAN:.,0,0,0,,The bath is open 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:49.45,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Oh, it is ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.15,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:55.77,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I'll take a relaxing bath and \Nrecover from the long day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:57.42,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Right, Big Sister ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:58.65,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:01.12,def2,.WOMAN:.,0,0,0,,Well,{Now,} please enjoy your stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:12.99,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,She looked like she was a little \Nsuspicious, didn't she, Big Sister ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:14.56,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:17.65,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,It might have worked three years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:21.42,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,...but now, it's a bit of a stretch to present ourselves as siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.90,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I wonder what we seemed like to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:29.35,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Who knows ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:47.45,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Keep it clean.{tidy.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:48.71,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I thought we bought two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:52.24,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,One of them is for Hide-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:55.99,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:04.20,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,You bought two T-shirts, too, right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:04.99,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:08.00,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,For a thing like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:11.42,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,What do you mean,\N "For a thing like this" ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.16,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:15.00,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,It's just that if we\N hadn't bought that stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.88,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,...we might have been able to get a taxi to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:21.16,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Are you trying to \Nsay this is my fault ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:28.44,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Not really. I just thought we might have gotten a taxi to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.65,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,You don't give up, do you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:33.17,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,You should be glad that \Nwe're not sleeping outdoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:34.64,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.29,def2,HIKIARI:,0,0,0,,I'm going to call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:41.13,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:46.80,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What does she plan to tell them{her family} ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:16.85,def2,MOTHER:.,0,0,0,,You missed the last train ?\NThe concert was that long ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:20.00,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Yeah. So I'll stay overnight tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:23.20,def2,MOTHER:.,0,0,0,,Honestly, you're so troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.55,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:28.65,def2,MOTHER:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}But Hiro is with you, right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:29.44,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:35.35,def2,MOTHER:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Okay then. Don't worry your parents too much, okay ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.90,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Sure. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:42.84,def2,MOTHER:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Oh, yes. You had a phone call, from Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:47.80,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HCDCCBC&\frz9.89\fscx157\fscy140\frx10\fry346\pos(308,371)}Yasui Inn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:44.99,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.22,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What did your mother say ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:12.40,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,About what ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:17.00,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,You explained to her why this happened, right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:19.65,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,The ring search, the \Nchildbirth incident, and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.81,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:26.93,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:32.59,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I just said that we missed the train, so we'd stay overnight. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:34.70,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:40.51,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I mean, the more I explain things,\Nthe more it sounds like an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:46.55,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,And your mother didn't say anything ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:50.38,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,She's not worried because you're with me, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:56.32,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Wasn't the last time we looked like siblings three years ago ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:08:00.93,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,To my mother, you're\Nlike a part of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.12,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:11.37,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I guess she doesn't understand how her daughter looks to boys our age.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.75,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,How do I look to them ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:16.51,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:28.37,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, well it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:36.00,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,...you're an attractive woman\Nwho makes men's hearts throb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:40.04,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,This is the first time \NI've been told that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.15,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What are you talking about ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:48.15,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Since junior high, you've received piles of love letters with corny phrases like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:50.65,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,By you, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:09:00.55,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HD0B5A8&\pos(106,81)}Yasui Inn
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:09:00.50,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Well, we were so close\N that I didn't see you clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:03.20,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,It's only recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:09.50,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,...that I started to vaguely understand why\N the guys around me were fussing over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.92,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I wasn't seeing you clearly, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:22.20,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Because you were too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:23.85,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,No !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:30.90,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:36.55,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,It was healing well, but because of this stupid concert, it's swelling up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:37.95,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,See ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.41,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Oh, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:41.20,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "it's true" ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:44.45,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Aren't you supposed to\Nworry or something ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:49.90,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,The bath here seems \Nto be good for bruises.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:52.49,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:58.25,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Then I'll go take a bath, Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.60,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&H88B7D6&\fscx147\fscy122\pos(329,154)}Large Public Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:06.20,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\move(112,360,112,89,10,3638)}Hot water
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:06.20,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\move(521,346,521,75,10,3638)}Hot water
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:06.20,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\move(377,451,373,295,20,2188)}{Men }Women
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:17.70,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,It's hot !
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:26.45,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Hm ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.30,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Uh, oh !
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:38.80,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's a mixed bath ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:44.23,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Is it the common setup...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:48.23,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...where there are separate entrances but they go to the same place ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:49.58,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}That means... {fantasizes}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:25.82,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:32.74,def2,.KINE:..,0,0,0,,Crap !
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:56.25,def2,.KINE:..,0,0,0,,So I missed the last train.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:12:03.15,def2,.KINE:..,0,0,0,,I didn't have enough money for a taxi, but I\Nhad enough to stay the night at a cheap inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:06.55,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:11.18,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,We came for the same concert, and ended up at the same inn for similar reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:12.27,def2,.KINE:..,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.30,def2,.KINE:..,0,0,0,,So who did you come with ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:18.48,def2,.KINE:..,0,0,0,,You didn't come here alone, did you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:20.61,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:26.10,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,It's Noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.10,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:28.96,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What about you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.65,def2,.KINE:..,0,0,0,,Don't ask such a thoughtless question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:37.80,def2,.KINE:..,0,0,0,,Do you think I would come this far for a concert with a guy ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:38.50,def2,.KINE:..,0,0,0,,Huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:44.25,def2,.KINE:..,0,0,0,,Don't tell anyone you saw me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:47.27,def2,.KINE:..,0,0,0,,Lots of girls will be\Nsad if they find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:49.34,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:52.20,def2,.KINE:..,0,0,0,,I'll get going, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:52.91,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:05.90,def2,.KINE:..,0,0,0,,Well, it probably goes without saying, but don't intrude on us, okay ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:08.32,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,No way I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.10,def2,.KINE:..,0,0,0,,You came here with a guy, huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.10,def2,.KINE:..,0,0,0,,I'm envious that you\Ncan be so carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:28.20,def2,.KINE:..,0,0,0,,Don't come peeping on us, okay ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.56,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,No way I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:50.54,def2,..MAN:..,0,0,0,,Hey, Kine. \NLend me a 100 yen coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:56.86,def2,..MAN:..,0,0,0,,I can't watch the porn channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:01.45,def2,..MAN:..,0,0,0,,100 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.30,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.00,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,That was such a long bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:49.40,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:56.70,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Can you get out of the way ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.85,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I want to get my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:03.90,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll watch some TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.72,def2,..TV:...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}{moaning noise} Silly !
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:17.10,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,You don't have to stop.{Help yourself without reservation.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:20.10,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Well, if I start to watch, I can't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.83,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Oh, is that how it is ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:35.61,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Do you want something to drink ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:36.63,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:43.09,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What's so good about this stuff ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:47.58,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,People who don't understand won't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:49.02,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I guess that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:07.91,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Do you want to use the brush ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:51.98,Karaoke Translation op,.SONG:..,0,0,0,,With each palm touching the other's, we walked in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:17:00.99,Karaoke Translation op,.SONG:..,0,0,0,,It's full of warmth, and we talked about lots of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:11.03,Karaoke Translation op,.SONG:..,0,0,0,,Being together shouldn't feel painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:20.80,Karaoke Translation op,.SONG:..,0,0,0,,Just keep carrying this brimming feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:30.39,Karaoke Translation op,.SONG:..,0,0,0,,There are many things where just\N being kind doesn't move us forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:42.51,Karaoke Translation op,.SONG:..,0,0,0,,But I don't hesitate to do things\Nfor you, and for the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:52.10,Karaoke Translation op,.SONG:..,0,0,0,,There will be a day when you can \Nsee love like a gentle rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:56.25,Karaoke Translation op,.SONG:..,0,0,0,,If you don't try to notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:18:01.65,Karaoke Translation op,.SONG:..,0,0,0,,...you'll overlook it, and you'll make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:11.20,Karaoke Translation op,.SONG:..,0,0,0,,As we repeat the laughing and smiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:19.61,Karaoke Translation op,.SONG:..,0,0,0,,...everyday that we can't relive is formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:49.24,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,You want the futons further apart ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:50.65,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:54.70,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Either way, I can't escape if you come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.67,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:19:01.65,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Back in the day, I could \Nbeat you in a sumo match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:04.55,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,But now, I don't stand\N a chance even if I resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.53,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:08.78,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Now, let's go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:24.55,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HD0B5A8&\fscx86\fscy72\move(441,410,588,404,0,4088)}Noda
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:34.30,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fscx88\fscy78\pos(267,243)}Yasui Inn
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:24.20,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}She feels safe falling asleep even though I'm right by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:32.75,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Nothing has changed\Nsince three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:40.59,def2,HARUKA:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Do you regret introducing Hikari to Tachibana ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:48.05,def2,KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Let's go to the Koushien, Manager{Haruka}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:47.63,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This is troubling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:53.79,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I can't sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:57.27,def2,HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...Hide-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:18.06,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:...,0,0,0,,{\pos(312.889,468.444)}If you have a hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:25.86,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(302.222,466.667)}...that I can hold forever as I walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.81,0:22:33.73,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(318.222,468.444)}I want you to let me hear you\N\N\Ncome closer and open the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.53,0:22:41.58,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(324.444,466.667)}...rather than the footsteps that\N\N\N sound further and further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:45.18,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(311.111,468.444)}The star I'm watching today...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.58,0:22:49.66,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(315.556,464.889)}...glistened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:55.28,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,467.556)}In the town full of things that disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:22:59.41,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(314.667,465.778)}...I thought to myself, wishfully:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.81,0:23:07.36,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(314.667,467.556)}Let's return to "two of us," let's return together...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.56,0:23:15.51,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(315.556,469.333)}...rather than losing our time to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:18.91,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,464.889)}Happiness is not something...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.34,0:23:23.74,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(313.778,466.667)}...that someone does for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.04,0:23:32.31,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(324.444,467.556)}It means that I have someone I can embrace.
